jif.types

Class LabelEquation

  • java.lang.Object
    • jif.types.Equation
      • jif.types.LabelEquation

  • public class LabelEquation
extends Equation
    Label equation derived from a label constraint. A label equation represents an inequality that must be satisfied, namely lhs <= rhs in the environment env.
    See Also:
    LabelConstraint
